\nc<>This is a place created so that believers can rest
comfortably during or after their activities.

\nc<>Vending machines, massage chairs, sofas, and other amenities
are fully equipped. I haven't used them myself, but I heard
there is also a bedroom in the back.

\nc<>...but it's better not to use this place as much as
possible...
\nc<Follower>Hey, Levantia! It's perfect timing. Wanna have some fun?

\nc<>Oh, Yasuo-kun. Sorry, but can you hold on for a moment? I'm
currently doing a promotional livestream for the Paradise
Church.
\nc<Follower>Oh, is that so? My apologies. I must have interrupted.

\ncEh? Levantia-chan, is there something different about you
today?

\nc<>Haha, there are days like that, right? How about taking
this opportunity to explain about the equipment?

\nc<>...The use of equipment is available to any believer of the
Paradise Church.

\nc<>Of course, not just the break room, but anytime in most
places within the church... huh!? ♡

\nc<>Um, um, it's hard to explain, so please move your hands for
a moment...

\ncHuh? What are you saying? Are the equipment refusing to be
used?
\nc<>No, I don't have... that kind of right...
\nc<>You can freely use the equipment like this... ah...♡

\nc<>However, conflicts between believers are prohibited, so when
the desired equipment is in use... until the other person
finishes... wait, ah...♡

\nc<>Oh my, even though you're supposed to be a magical girl,
it's pathetic that you can't even give a proper explanation
just because your breasts were touched a little.

\nc<>Well, I guess there's no helping it. Now that we're done
explaining the break room, let's move on to the next
location.
\nc<>Yasuo-kun, please handle it with other equipment.
